      <scopecontent id="aspace_d2edfa41e6a550fdba874bab8d05e20c">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of reunion photographs; a letter from the class secretary, Charles S. Miller; and addresses of class members maintained by Arthur Wells Cole documenting the Yale College Class of 1877. Included is Cole's account book while a student at Yale.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
